Ovulation & Cycle Calendar

Oohvie is your personal Period Tracker and Ovulation Calendar designed with you in mind. Accurate, AI-based tracking of your period lets you plan for future events, determine safe times for sexual activity, prepare for a future pregnancy, and monitor any period irregularities.

Created for women by experienced women’s health professionals, Oohvie is the only menstrual cycle app that offers a comprehensive approach to women’s healthcare - including a 1:1 Nurse Chat and Telemedicine Connection through HealthLynked.

Your health is more than just dates on a calendar. Start your journey to personalized healthcare with a full-solution women’s health tool designed with your optimal health in mind.


PERIOD TRACKER
Take the mystery out of your monthly menstrual cycle. Log your periods, symptoms, and moods to track your personal health trends. Use Oohvie to track any abnormalities in your cycle and gain insights on your health.


OVULATION CALENDAR
Find the best time to get pregnant with Oohvie's AI-based ovulation calendar. Know when to plan and pace intercourse and reach your family planning goals faster. Get pregnancy planning support and tips from other expecting mothers on Oohvie's Community Forum and Private Chat.


OOHVIE’S ONLINE NURSE CHAT
You asked and we listened. Introducing Oohvie’s Online Nurse Chat! Update your Oohvie app and chat 1:1 with a nurse any time between 9:00am and 5:00pm EST. Oohvie’s nurses can provide you with personalized answers to your health questions or guide you to the right resources.


SYMPTOM & MOOD LOG
Know yourself and your body better. Log your moods and symptoms throughout the month as a part of your daily health journal.


HEALTHLYNKED PROFILE & DOCLYNK TELEMEDICINE CONNECTION
Only Oohvie incorporates your menstrual cycle data into your healthcare records by automatically sending your information to your free HealthLynked Patient Profile through our secure, cloud-based system.

Use your HealthLynked profile to find a doctor near you, schedule virtual appointments, securely store and share medical records, and connect Oohvie to share your personal menstrual data with your OB/GYN.


CUSTOMIZABLE PILL & WELLNESS REMINDERS

COMMUNITY FORUM & PRIVATE CHAT
Find a topic that interests you in Oohvie’s Women's Health Forum or find a new friend to connect with. Get support from women around the country and securely chat with Oohvie’s Private Chat feature.


WOMEN’S HEALTH NEWS
Find articles about the health topics that matter to you most. Learn more about your body and get tips you can trust from Oohvie’s healthcare professionals.


SHOP FEMININE CARE PRODUCTS
Get discounted brand-name tampons, pads, menstrual cups, and liners that are shipped discreetly to your home, right in the app. Shop Oohvie branded apparel and accessories for your lifestyle.


SECURE & AD-FREE
We take your private health information seriously. That’s why Oohvie does not and will never share or sell your data to advertisers. Oohvie is an ad-free health platform.
